HEADWORD: Superabundance
<hw>Su`per*a*bun"dance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>superabundantia</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>superabondance</ets>.]</ety>
<def>The quality or state of being superabundant; a superabundant
quantity; redundancy; excess.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

